<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Me</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), -10px -10px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #333;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        main {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 10px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .neumorphism-card {
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 10px 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), -10px -10px 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            padding: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 200px;
            display: inline-flexbox;
            margin: 60px 60px;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .neumorphism-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 100%;
            height: 30px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin: 20px auto;
            box-shadow: inset 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), inset -5px -5px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .progress-bar-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background-color: #434343;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: inset 3px 3px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), inset -3px -3px 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transition: width 0.5s ease;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .progress-bar p {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .neumorphism-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #101010;
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: inset 5px 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset -5px -5px 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .neumorphism-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: inset 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3), inset -2px -2px 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/projects">Projects</a></li>
            <li><a href="/services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>
<main>
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <p>I am passionate at Web & App developement with experience in Node.js, Express.js, Flutter and more!
        Currently pursuing a Bachelor of Science in Computer Science & Engineering, 
        I possess a keen interest in the intersection of technology and design. 
        Proficient in graphics design, I enjoy leveraging my creativity to complement my technical education. 
        
    </p>
      <button class="neumorphism-button" onclick="openImage()">CV</button>
    <div class="neumorphism-card">
        <h2>Skills</h2>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            <p>HTML</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            <p>CSS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 80%;"></div>
            <p>JavaScript</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 70%;"></div>
            <p>Flutter</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 40%;"></div>
            <p>PHP</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            <p>Illustrator</p>
        </div>
        <div class="progress-bar">
            <div class="progress-bar-fill" style="width: 100%;"></div>
            <p>Photoshop</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  
</main>
<script>
  
    window.addEventListener('mousemove', function (e) {
        const x = e.clientX / window.innerWidth;
        const y = e.clientY / window.innerHeight;
        document.body.style.background = `radial-gradient(at ${x * 100}% ${y * 100}%, rgba(255,255,255,0.5), rgba(255,255,255,0))`;
    });

    function openImage() {
        window.open('image/CV.jpg', '_blank'); 
    }
</script>
</body>
</html>
